title: THE WAY OF THE WARRIOR #2
itunes:title: THE WAY OF THE WARRIOR #2
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
"There's a power inside of you that makes you unstoppable. The flesh of the warrior is vulnerable, but the mind is and spirit inside of the champion is a savage force of undeniable will. Scarred and wounded the warrior is not undeterred, alone he fights, blinded by darkness, but still he is not deterred." – Billy Alsbrooks ((https://bit.ly/BillyAlsbrooksMotiversity)


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic).
